WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.314
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.314 --> 00:00:02.674
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:02.674 --> 00:00:04.480
We're going to pray about some things.

00:00:04.480 --> 00:00:08.702
But I'm going to tell you, it's time for the church to wake up.

00:00:08.702 --> 00:00:44.604
In this thing that I've seen taking place, I've seen a church—the blood-bought, born-again, blood-bought church of the redeemed—standing up in brush arbor churches, and a righteousness and a holiness being preached back in the pulpits again with people that are humbled and weeping at the altar, crying out for a sovereign God, what they would call a God of repentance, a God of recompense to restore back what the cankerworm ate, to call back, and we would have a harvest of souls.

00:00:46.747 --> 00:00:56.590
Not so much financially motivated, but glory-motivated—a glorious motivation of just saying, 'We're so all out.

00:00:56.590 --> 00:00:58.186
We're sold out for Jesus.

00:00:58.186 --> 00:01:05.839
' We want a new touch from the Father in these brush arbor churches; we want the glory.

00:01:05.839 --> 00:01:12.355
We want a manifestation of His glory, but it will not come with a dirty people.

00:01:12.355 --> 00:01:16.210
You can say what you want to, but your church is dirty.

00:01:16.210 --> 00:01:21.342
And the people don't have a heart after Him.

00:01:21.342 --> 00:01:24.293
They do not have a heart after the Father.

00:01:24.293 --> 00:01:27.760
A lot of them have a heart after the world.

00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:35.440
And the Lord says, 'Either you are hot or you're cold, but if you're lukewarm, I will spew you out of my mouth.

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:36.994
' And you say, 'Well, that's harsh.

00:01:36.994 --> 00:01:38.996
' No, it's the word.

00:01:38.996 --> 00:01:44.885
And it's going to come down to it: you are going to preach the word, not an opinion.

00:01:44.885 --> 00:01:50.320
And we either stand by the word or you get out of the pulpit.

00:01:50.320 --> 00:02:04.936
It's time that we rise up like Davids and take the land and know that it's going to take a bulldog personality to say, 'We're going to stand for Jesus—all for Jesus, all for Him or nothing else.

00:02:04.936 --> 00:02:08.079
' You think, 'Well, we're just going to limp by.

00:02:08.279 --> 00:02:14.140
We're going to get back in there and we're going to preach them a little bit of soft, limp, little spoonful of gospel and just kind of nourish people.

00:02:14.140 --> 00:02:17.049
' No, it's going to take a bunch of meat-eaters.

00:02:24.524 --> 00:02:26.147
You say, 'Well, I'm vegan.

00:02:26.147 --> 00:02:28.239
' I don't care if you're vegan or not.

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:28.599
Whatever.

00:02:28.599 --> 00:02:32.891
I'm talking about people who have teeth that eat the meat of the word.

00:02:32.891 --> 00:02:36.971
Not a vegan word; I'm talking about the meat of the word.

00:02:36.971 --> 00:03:07.110
I'm talking about people getting some common sense here and knowing that you've got to preach righteousness and you've got to preach holiness and get it back in the pulpits and telling people they've got to rise up and tell that Jesus Christ is coming, for the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few, and the house of cards is coming down, folks.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:09.333
Jesus is coming.

00:03:09.333 --> 00:03:12.148
Are you ready for His return?

00:03:12.148 --> 00:03:20.091
There's many of you who say that you are, but He has no idea who you are because you're so far from Him.

00:03:20.091 --> 00:03:30.170
You live such a heathen lifestyle and you don't even realize that you are like Lot in Sodom and Gomorrah thinking that everything's okay.

00:03:30.170 --> 00:03:39.582
And it took Abraham interceding for Lot in the midst of Gomorrah, crying out to spare Lot and his family.

00:03:39.582 --> 00:03:43.109
One man stood in the gap, like I told you.

00:03:43.109 --> 00:03:47.600
One person stood in the gap for the person as Lot and his family.

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:55.920
And if he wouldn't have been standing in the gap, Lot would have been burned up just like everybody else was.

00:03:55.920 --> 00:04:02.899
He didn't even know judgment was coming because he'd become so familiar with Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:04:02.899 --> 00:04:10.743
He did not know that all the things were coming because he was so in compromise.

00:04:10.743 --> 00:04:18.199
He fixed his tent towards Sodom and he thought, 'Man, this is a nice city.

00:04:21.340 --> 00:04:22.490
I love living in this.

00:04:22.490 --> 00:04:23.460
This is nice.

00:04:23.460 --> 00:04:26.960
' And every day he woke up seeing all around him.

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.497
And as he did, he became colder and colder.

00:04:29.497 --> 00:04:37.199
And it took a man standing on the hill saying, 'Would you spare them?

00:04:37.199 --> 00:04:40.100
' And God had mercy and removed his family.

00:04:40.100 --> 00:04:44.978
But his wife was so familiar she looked back and she turned to a pillar of salt.

00:04:44.978 --> 00:04:53.759
Will you be one that turns to a pillar of salt as you're crying out for that which was so important around you?

00:04:53.759 --> 00:04:55.817
Everything is so important to you.

00:04:55.817 --> 00:05:00.230
I hear the Spirit of the Lord say, 'But am I important to you?

00:05:00.230 --> 00:05:02.380
Am I important to you?

00:05:02.380 --> 00:05:17.147
' says the Lord as your house of cards begins to crumble, just like Lot's wife turned and looked to Sodom and it was so important to her because she had become so accustomed to it.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:20.986
You've become accustomed to Sodom and Gomorrah, ladies and gentlemen.

00:05:20.986 --> 00:05:25.622
And the Lord tells me, 'Great judgment's coming in these areas.

00:05:25.622 --> 00:05:28.337
' And you say, 'Well, I'll stand in the gap like Abraham.

00:05:28.337 --> 00:05:30.731
' But God's calling you out from Sodom.

00:05:30.731 --> 00:05:33.269
God's calling you out from Gomorrah.

00:05:33.269 --> 00:05:42.300
He's calling you out and He's telling you it's time to come up higher or you're going to stay back here and turn to that pillar of salt.

00:05:49.139 --> 00:05:57.066
Are you going to turn your back on Sodom and Gomorrah just like Lot had to and run to the mountains with the angels, or are you going to keep looking back because it was familiar to you and you got accustomed to it?

00:05:57.066 --> 00:06:00.039
I'm telling you, it's time to come out of that.

00:06:00.039 --> 00:06:10.056
It's time to come up in the glory and sit at His altar and weep before Him and say, 'Jesus, all of You and none of me.

00:06:10.056 --> 00:06:12.373
All of You and none of me.

00:06:17.554 --> 00:06:18.057
I don't want any of this world.

00:06:22.399 --> 00:06:23.159
I don't want to be so spiritually minded that I'm no earthly good.

00:06:23.159 --> 00:06:27.250
' Some people say, 'I don't see that you could be too spiritually minded, folks.

00:06:27.250 --> 00:06:32.147
' You say, 'I don't want to be too spiritually minded.

00:06:33.693 --> 00:06:37.076
I don't want to be too spiritual because I won't be able to relate with Sodom.

00:06:39.622 --> 00:06:39.919
I want to relate with Sodom.

00:06:40.1000 --> 00:06:59.449
I want to relate with Gomorrah because I want to be able to minister to them because if I get too spiritual and I get too holy roller on you, we won't be able to minister because they won't be able to relate with us.

00:06:59.449 --> 00:07:00.530
' You're wrong.

00:07:00.530 --> 00:07:01.380
You're wrong.

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:04.787
He's calling us to be the salt of the earth.

00:07:04.787 --> 00:07:08.330
He's calling us to have a backbone like a crowbar.

00:07:21.096 --> 00:07:21.405
And He's calling us to preach the good news to the world.

00:07:31.479 --> 00:07:37.039
And I'm telling you, when all hell breaks out, ladies and gentlemen, when all crap hits the fan, they're going to be coming for the people who have the light, like Moses' face was shining with the glory of God.

00:07:37.039 --> 00:08:02.960
They're going to come to you because they're going to say, 'I remember when I used to think you were a holy roller and you were too religious, because right now I need a God that's real, right now because of all the hell that's going on around me and the economy's crashing and the people are getting sick and dying.

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:04.760
I need a God that's real.

00:08:05.570 --> 00:08:08.439
Not a God that is a lukewarm God.

00:08:24.400 --> 00:08:24.735
Not a God that I have my tent fixed to Sodom because I want to be just a little bit like them so I'm relatable.

00:08:24.735 --> 00:08:27.080
I want to be like Jesus.

00:08:31.310 --> 00:08:31.520
And there was no compromise in Him at all.

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:38.640
He was the rock and upon Him He said, 'You will build my church and the gates of hell will not prevail against it.

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:52.320
' Not a sinking sand gospel, but a gospel that is built on the word, the foundation of the word that Jesus Christ is coming and that Jesus is our Savior.

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:53.691
He's our Healer.

00:08:53.691 --> 00:08:55.020
He's our Deliverer.

00:08:55.020 --> 00:08:57.440
And He is not a compromising God.

00:09:11.611 --> 00:09:11.977
That is just a lukewarm, spoonful gospel.

00:09:11.977 --> 00:09:16.879
We're going to just barely feed you, and you're going to get your little baby pampers...

00:09:20.300 --> 00:09:20.600
No, no, no.

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:30.940
It's time to feed the meat of the word to the people so that they're able to stand and stand when all there else to do is stand.

00:09:30.940 --> 00:09:35.320
Therefore, it's time to stand and have a backbone in this generation.

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:36.857
Woe to you that don't.

00:09:36.857 --> 00:09:38.649
You're going to go home early.

00:09:38.649 --> 00:09:40.709
I'm telling you.

00:09:40.709 --> 00:09:43.573
Woe to you who don't because you'll go home early.

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:51.499
You won't be able to stand because the devourer is coming for you.

00:10:12.900 --> 00:10:13.235
The great devourer will come for you.

00:10:13.235 --> 00:10:18.924
Satan comes as a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:10:19.742 --> 00:10:22.765
Is your house full of compromise that he can devour you?

00:10:22.765 --> 00:10:27.645
Because as for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:10:48.824 --> 00:10:49.279
And we have a bloodline out there that says, 'Satan, thus far and no further.

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:52.160
' You will not tread on us.

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:54.959
We tread on you.

00:10:54.959 --> 00:10:58.530
We have authority over you in this house.

00:10:58.530 --> 00:11:01.504
Do you have that authority in your house?

00:11:01.504 --> 00:11:05.698
Are you still in Sodom and Gomorrah and you think you're okay?

00:11:05.698 --> 00:11:12.360
Because I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, there's a lot of you that are in there.

00:11:18.433 --> 00:11:18.920
I hear this by the Spirit of God.

00:11:23.075 --> 00:11:23.626
You better be listening for what I have seen coming.

00:11:23.626 --> 00:11:32.996
If you are in Sodom and there's somebody out there—your grandma is out there praying for you, 'Oh, have mercy on Johnny out there'—you better thank God for her.

00:11:32.996 --> 00:11:37.824
'Oh, have mercy on little Susie' or whoever because they're up there: 'Lord, please have mercy.

00:11:37.824 --> 00:11:39.615
Please have mercy.

00:11:39.615 --> 00:11:46.311
' And you're in there just partying in Sodom, 'I'm over here just enjoying myself.

00:11:46.311 --> 00:11:48.800
' You're a fool.

00:12:03.093 --> 00:12:05.959
God have mercy on you.

00:12:19.420 --> 00:12:19.804
The angels of the Lord are sent to protect them.

00:12:24.098 --> 00:12:25.787
I don't know who this is for today, but I pray it stirs you.

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:38.720
I don't want to be too spiritually minded that I'm no earthly good.

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:40.000
God have mercy on you.

00:12:45.422 --> 00:12:45.684
I'm all in.

00:12:45.684 --> 00:12:46.995
Are you all in?

00:12:46.995 --> 00:12:48.120
Are you all in for Jesus?

00:12:48.120 --> 00:12:48.1000
All to Jesus, I surrender.

00:12:48.1000 --> 00:12:50.861
All to Him, I freely give.

00:12:51.093 --> 00:12:55.120
I've seen a great storm coming and it's still on the horizon.

00:12:55.120 --> 00:13:03.200
It may be delayed by some months, whether or not it's a year or whatever.

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:09.130
When you're looking into the spirit realm, ladies and gentlemen, there's a depth perception about things that I'm still learning.

00:13:16.930 --> 00:13:17.140
But I can assure you, I see a storm on the horizon.

00:13:18.189 --> 00:13:26.960
And I'm telling you, it's a time like never before to fall at the altars, falling at Jesus' feet and saying, 'All to Jesus, I surrender.

00:13:26.960 --> 00:13:30.849
All to Thee, I humbly give.

00:13:38.399 --> 00:13:38.586
I give You my heart.

00:13:41.770 --> 00:13:42.220
I give You my soul.

00:13:42.220 --> 00:13:48.315
' Today, Lord, I serve You with everything I have inside of me.

00:13:54.044 --> 00:13:55.596
I am not worried and I'm not moved by what I see around me.

00:13:55.596 --> 00:13:59.630
I'm moved by what the Word of God says.

00:13:59.630 --> 00:14:07.146
Because when the winds and the storms blow, my anchor is in the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:14:09.629 --> 00:14:11.360
My eyes are fixed upon You.

00:14:11.360 --> 00:14:14.649
The anchor of my soul is in Jesus.

00:14:16.610 --> 00:14:27.618
No matter when the winds and the waves of life try to knock me down, my anchor is in You.

00:14:27.618 --> 00:14:30.740
I'm anchored in You.

00:14:30.740 --> 00:14:33.664
I'm anchored in the presence and the fire of God.

00:14:38.331 --> 00:14:38.663
And I'm telling you all, it's time to wake up.

00:14:38.663 --> 00:14:41.130
I'm telling you, I've seen it again.

00:14:54.578 --> 00:14:54.867
So, I hope this message is sobering to you.

00:14:54.867 --> 00:14:56.022
That's my job.

00:14:56.022 --> 00:14:58.088
The Lord said, 'Know your audience.

00:14:58.981 --> 00:15:00.399
My audience is you all.

00:15:00.399 --> 00:15:06.504
' And I pray with all my heart that this struck home today.

00:15:06.504 --> 00:15:08.352
Do not just throw it away.

00:15:08.352 --> 00:15:12.420
Don't just sit there and go, 'Well, it's not for me.

00:15:12.420 --> 00:15:13.160
' No, it's for you.

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:21.440
All to Jesus, I surrender.

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:28.420
So, if you don't know Jesus Christ today as your Lord and personal Savior, it's your time to come home.

00:15:28.420 --> 00:15:36.639
I'm going to say a prayer and I want you to pray it out loud.

00:15:38.845 --> 00:15:40.212
You say, 'Brother Brandon, I don't know Jesus Christ.

00:15:40.212 --> 00:15:42.826
I've heard a lot about Him.

00:15:42.826 --> 00:15:46.846
' But if you die tonight, where will you spend eternity?

00:15:46.846 --> 00:15:49.259
There's a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:15:49.259 --> 00:15:51.680
Who will you serve today?

00:15:51.680 --> 00:15:56.205
That's what I'm trying to ask you all, ladies and gentlemen.

00:15:56.205 --> 00:16:02.339
Either you're going to serve Jesus or you're going to serve the devil.

00:16:02.339 --> 00:16:05.485
But you can't ride the line and try to be both.

00:16:05.485 --> 00:16:08.079
It's time to sell out for Jesus today.

00:16:08.079 --> 00:16:11.368
It's time for you to give it all to Jesus.

00:16:11.368 --> 00:16:14.170
Make Him the Lord of your life.

00:16:14.170 --> 00:16:18.720
I pray a conviction in your heart to come to the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:16:18.720 --> 00:16:28.909
Now, I'm going to say a prayer for you, and I want you to repeat this prayer after me: 'Jesus Christ, I want to make You my Lord and personal Savior.

00:16:28.909 --> 00:16:31.467
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:16:31.467 --> 00:16:32.578
Father, I'm a sinner.

00:16:32.578 --> 00:16:33.733
Forgive me of my sins.

00:16:33.733 --> 00:16:35.759
I believe You are the Son of God.

00:16:51.431 --> 00:16:51.716
I believe You rose on the third day.

00:16:51.716 --> 00:16:55.049
I believe You're seated at the Father's right hand making intercession for me.

00:16:55.049 --> 00:16:58.177
Now, I thank You, Lord, that You forgive me of my sins.

00:16:58.177 --> 00:16:59.428
I thank You.

00:16:59.428 --> 00:17:00.971
I've been a sinner.

00:17:00.971 --> 00:17:02.066
Lord, forgive me.

00:17:02.066 --> 00:17:04.940
I don't want to be a sinner no more.

00:17:04.940 --> 00:17:05.590
I run to You.

00:17:05.590 --> 00:17:07.104
I surrender to You.

00:17:21.262 --> 00:17:21.600
I give all to You.

00:17:21.600 --> 00:17:23.040
Cleanse me from all unrighteousness.

00:17:23.040 --> 00:17:25.220
I want to come up higher.

00:17:25.220 --> 00:17:27.839
I want to be born again today.

00:17:27.839 --> 00:17:31.360
' It doesn't have to be religious, ladies and gentlemen.

00:17:42.498 --> 00:17:42.720
We make it religious.

00:17:46.039 --> 00:17:49.909
Jesus wants it to be just as a child can come before Him and get born again.

00:17:49.909 --> 00:17:52.720
A child can do it.

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:56.180
A child doesn't know an extensive vocabulary.

00:17:56.180 --> 00:17:58.450
A child just knows little stuff.

00:17:58.450 --> 00:18:02.000
But He made it so that a child can get born again.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:04.824
He didn't say, 'Come to me as my spiritual adults.

00:18:04.824 --> 00:18:06.000
' Come to me as children.

00:18:09.440 --> 00:18:09.760
And He's my Abba Father.

00:18:09.760 --> 00:18:11.039
He's my God.

00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:21.090
And I come to Him daily and I say, 'Father, I love You.

00:18:21.090 --> 00:18:23.003
' And He says, 'I love you, too.

00:18:23.003 --> 00:18:39.460
' So if you said the prayer today and you believed in your heart and you confessed your sins and you believed it with all you have—you believe that Jesus Christ rose again on the third day and He died for you—I believe today you got saved.

00:18:39.460 --> 00:18:41.966
Now find a Bible that you understand.

00:18:47.931 --> 00:18:48.206
It doesn't have to be King James.

00:18:48.206 --> 00:18:51.220
Find a Bible that you understand and read it.

00:18:51.220 --> 00:18:54.148
Get the word of God down in your heart.

00:18:56.658 --> 00:19:01.010
And when you get that word down inside of your heart, it's going to change you and you'll go from glory to glory.

00:19:01.010 --> 00:19:02.050
Pray every day.

00:19:02.050 --> 00:19:03.500
Seek Him every day.

00:19:03.500 --> 00:19:11.299
Have a relationship with Him every day.

00:19:11.299 --> 00:19:14.969
And find a good Bible-believing church in your area.

00:19:14.969 --> 00:19:15.964
Get plugged in.

00:19:15.964 --> 00:19:16.960
Find a pastor.

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:24.400
Tell them, 'I got born again online and I gave my heart to Jesus Christ on this day and I want to be baptized.

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:26.276
' Go and get baptized at church.

00:19:26.276 --> 00:19:28.914
Go and find a church that preaches the gospel.

00:19:28.914 --> 00:19:33.829
Get plugged in—usher, pray, whatever you can do to volunteer.

00:19:33.829 --> 00:19:34.514
Take classes.

00:19:34.514 --> 00:19:36.520
Learn about who you are.

00:19:36.520 --> 00:19:39.679
Find classes to teach you the word.

00:19:42.559 --> 00:19:46.205
And when you do this, you're going to grow and you'll become like a meat eater.

00:19:46.205 --> 00:19:53.066
I'm talking about eating the meat of the word so that you're able to have a backbone.

00:19:53.066 --> 00:19:56.475
It's easy to be a Christian, folks.

00:19:56.475 --> 00:20:00.960
Having the Christian walk sometimes is challenging, but it's easy to stay saved.

00:20:00.960 --> 00:20:03.679
It's easy to come before Him.

00:20:03.679 --> 00:20:06.880
He made it so a child could.

00:20:06.880 --> 00:20:09.360
So that's what I had for that.

00:20:09.360 --> 00:20:12.046
Now, we're going to pray for the election.

00:20:12.046 --> 00:20:17.486
But the Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, you got to take this more serious.

00:20:17.486 --> 00:20:19.840
You got to tell these people what's coming.

00:20:19.840 --> 00:20:26.784
' And they're not going to like it, but I'm going to tell you the truth.

00:20:26.784 --> 00:20:30.571
So, Father, we thank You for the body.

00:20:43.139 --> 00:20:43.529
We take communion as a body of believers together.

00:20:44.579 --> 00:20:53.417
For this is what He did: He died and He rose again on the third day and He became sickness for us.

00:20:53.417 --> 00:20:57.239
And as we take this body, we take it inside of us.

00:21:03.520 --> 00:21:22.480
And I believe with all my heart, it's the meal that heals; that every cell inside of me is healed and whole and well because He said in Isaiah 53:5 that He was wounded for our transgressions, He was bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon Him and with His stripes you are healed.

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:25.440
You are healed because He took all of it on.

00:21:33.039 --> 00:21:33.289
And we take this body right now in the name of Jesus.

00:21:33.289 --> 00:21:38.186
Now Lord, this is all I have is this peach tea stuff today.

00:21:38.453 --> 00:21:40.510
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:21:49.210 --> 00:21:49.460
